{"tid":361654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟基督徒林子健去耶魯係exchange定真係耶魯收佢讀神學？","createTime":"2017-08-16T10:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:51:28.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b1a4b8b37030fdf95d88e413f34ef19326b4d6","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"本院（崇基神學院）成立至今，竭力以本地關懷出發，匯通中西神學學術，讓師生、牧者等接觸多元傳統，建立全球視野，致力於與國內外學術機構建立常設夥伴及交流平台。自2010年起，本院與耶魯大學神學院(Yale Divinity School)設立交流計劃。每年雙方可派學生作一學期或一學年的交流學習，亦設有老師的交流計劃。<br />\n<br />\nsource:舊登"},{"pid":"c3c959e4987ed9d27636a888ab35aabf1e5731ba","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da147a23ee21b9e2d9f31409d693d7bb380d6d7","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0ff37c6e3ad3dc7a0eef41c76fe66efb95489a","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1ac2dffb5ebfa0c7fd0f180aac1b73edfd61af","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db2ff8045754cbe5fc3d072eb49acb922227d27","tid":361654,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"無人理我"},{"pid":"f4f724aabc9e47e7afd172f7dd309ee3c6459d04","tid":361654,"uid":68160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人理我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個名！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n釘他十字架！"},{"pid":"8fe87538b1fdac6c761a4f609556e70e711ef956","tid":361654,"uid":2